116
00:07:16,650 --> 00:07:18,220
Yeah.

117
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:38,500
It's so beautiful.

118
00:07:39,030 --> 00:07:39,880
Yeah...

119
00:07:41,100 --> 00:07:42,120
Alright.

120
00:07:42,530 --> 00:07:46,380
