123
00:07:56,470 --> 00:07:57,470
A wish?

124
00:07:58,200 --> 00:07:59,200
Yep.

125
00:08:01,130 --> 00:08:02,130
Oh.

126
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,540
I win.

127
00:08:04,930 --> 00:08:05,800
Yeah.

128
00:08:07,980 --> 00:08:09,280
My wish is...

129
00:08:10,360 --> 00:08:11,690
