153
00:10:07,450 --> 00:10:08,680
I told you it's dangerous!

154
00:10:08,860 --> 00:10:10,060
Then just take it.

155
00:10:19,110 --> 00:10:20,110
Um...

156
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:23,180
I...

